What is NPRO

NPRO is the utility token that powers the growth and innovation of the NEAR Mobile Wallet. Its main purpose is to accelerate adoption of the NEAR ecosystem, with a focus on long-term sustainability and enhanced user experience.

NPRO not only enhances the wallet experience, but also promotes a more active, accessible, and aligned ecosystem with NEAR’s decentralized vision. With real incentives and a clear utility structure, it serves as a bridge between usability and sustainable growth.

NPRO Fair Launch and Token Release

Release

Every epoch, a specific amount of NPRO tokens will be released and fully allocated to users staking NEAR with the NEAR Mobile Validator.

The allocation is done in proportion to each user's share of the total staked NEAR, ensuring a fair and balanced reward distribution based on participation. The system is designed to reward long-term participation.

Early stakers have an advantage, as the daily token release is higher at the beginning, and with fewer people competing, you get a larger share.

Bonding curve

The amount of NPRO tokens released will decrease every epoch following a bonding curve model, with a decay parameter of 0.00023664977144416. This parameter has been set to ensure that the amount of NPRO released in the last epoch is 25% of the amount released in the first epoch which is 1892. This provides a balanced approach, rewarding early adopters while keeping the rewards interesting throughout the 5-year period.

This mechanism also creates natural scarcity as the token becomes progressively harder to obtain. This scarcity mechanism enhances the long-term value proposition for investors by increasing the difficulty of obtaining new tokens over time. This scarcity, combined with the required holdings to unlock premium features and the liquidity mechanism that generates upward price pressure, positions as NPRO as a strong investment opportunity.

Additionally, the token liquidity mechanism has been designed to ensure that even if 45% of recipients sell their tokens immediately and no new buyers emerge, the token’s price will still experience upward pressure, demonstrating the resilience of the system.

NEAR backed value

NEAR staking rewards are used to purchase NPRO from the liquidity pool and then added back as liquidity. As a result, the token’s value is intrinsically linked to NEAR’s performance. If NEAR’s price increases, NPRO’s price is also expected to rise due to this close integration of staking rewards and liquidity mechanics.

Price appreciation

Regular purchases from the liquidity pool generate upward pressure on NPRO's price.

Liquidity Stability

Adding liquidity helps reduce volatility and makes NPRO more resilient to price shocks.

Initial Lockup for Liquidity Building

During the first three months, NPRO tokens distributed to stakers will be locked in a smart contract to build liquidity and stabilize initial price dynamics before public trading begins. This period helps to establish a robust foundation for NPRO's market liquidity and price.The NEAR Mobile team will not receive any of the released NPRO tokens directly. This ensures that all rewards are directed towards community members, fostering trust and fairness.

The LP tokens of the liquidity pool will be burned to ensure that the liquidity added to the pool cannot be removed. This guarantees that the liquidity remains in place permanently, providing security to token holders and ensuring that no one can perform a rug pull by removing the liquidity.

Upward pressure liquidity algorithm

As NPRO tokens are released and NEAR staking rewards are received, half of the NEAR staking rewards will be used to purchase NPRO from the liquidity pool. The remaining half is paired with the purchased NPRO and added as liquidity to the pool. This process naturally increases liquidity depth while also driving upward price pressure.

Notably, the NEAR staking rewards used in this mechanism back the value of NPRO, ensuring a tangible and direct linkage to NEAR’s price. Unlike many projects that launch tokens out of thin air, this design ensures that NPRO has intrinsic value derived from staking rewards.

No risk

NPRO carries no risk because it is derived solely from staking rewards generated by holding NEAR tokens. Users are not required to give up or spend their original NEAR holdings—instead, they retain full ownership of their initial NEAR at all times. The rewards are simply a byproduct of securing the network through staking, meaning users receive the token as an additional benefit without putting their principal at risk.

When you stake NEAR, you keep full ownership of your NEAR.

Key Benefits and Utility

NPRO tokens grant access to tiered membership levels within the NEAR Mobile wallet, unlocking progressively advanced features. Each level requires holding a certain amount of NPRO to access:

Basic Tier

Access essential wallet features: manage 1 wallet, buy, send, receive, stake, swap with Intents any token, and explore multichain capabilities. No NPRO required—ideal for casual users.

Ambassador Tier

Unlocks extra functionality: up to 2 wallets + management, reduced fees on swap (0.656% fee →25% discount) and staking (2.5% fee), token investor info, token price notifications, Basic App customization. Designed for active community members and early supporters.

Premium Tier

Full access to premium features: Unlimited addresses, reduced fee swap (0.218% fee → 75% discount) and staking (0% fee), portfolio analytics, portfolio notifications, downloadable statements, private support and advanced customization. Built for power users and DeFi pros.

Roadmap

Q2 2025

NEAR Intents go live natively. NEAR Mobile becomes multichain. NPRO announced. Full app refactor sets the stage for monthly feature rollouts.

Q3 2025

NPRO prelaunch begins. Earn tokens via referrals and missions. Pre-staking campaign launches. Monthly updates continue, expanding utility and community rewards.

Q4 2025

NPRO launches. Unlock premium features: price alerts, manage multiple addresses, advanced DeFi tools inside NEAR Mobile, private support and app customization

Frequent answers

Check frequent asked questions about NPRO below

What is NPRO and what does it unlock?

NPRO is the utility token of NEAR Mobile. It unlocks premium wallet features like price alerts, cashback, and advanced DeFi functionality based on your tier.

How can I get NPRO?

The primary way to earn NPRO is by staking NEAR through NEAR Mobile—you retain full access to your funds while earning rewards. Additional tokens can be earned by completing missions and referring friends, but staking remains the main path to participation. No presale, no insiders.

When will NPRO launch?

NPRO officially launched was 15th December 2025, and is available in NEAR Mobile wallet, NEAR Intents and Rhea Finance. Follow us on X and join our Discord to stay up to date on earning campaigns.

Is NPRO Safe?

Yes. NPRO is earned primarily by staking NEAR—you keep full access to your NEAR while earning rewards, making it a low-risk way to participate. It’s built by the team behind NEAR Mobile, one of the top wallets in the ecosystem, and contributors to key NEAR infrastructure like FastAuth and OneClickConnect.

What makes NPRO different from other crypto tokens?

NPRO is backed by real NEAR staking rewards, has no presale, and is tied to actual in-app utility. It features a fair launch, community-focused tokenomics with most supply going to user rewards—and LP tokens are burned to reinforce long-term trust and stability.
